data.text: Set your reminders for our Twitter spaces 🫡⏰🔥 we’ll see you there if we don’t catch you on the live stream! https://t.co/EXDqRXWkMw

Join us a Twitter Live Stream on Dec. 12th at 5:00 PM EDT to get a platform walkthrough, learn about protocol design, and hear about some of our $APE lending partners 👀 from @yuboruan and @DRodriguezFX  🔥 

After the live stream, we’ll be hopping on Twitter Spaces for an AMA 🙌 https://t.co/UYUYplUAsb

Additional features we will be implementing over the coming weeks include: notification sign-ups for borrow rates vs reward rates, as well as upgrading to a time locked contract for additional security and upgradability 🔐 🔥

https://t.co/r86sEv4Oes

ParaSpace supports these ERC-721 collections: @BoredApeYC, #MAYC, @OthersideMeta, @Azuki, @MeebitsNFTs, @moonbirds, @cryptopunksnfts, @doodles, and #CloneX

ERC-20 support for: $ETH, $wETH, $DAI, $USDC, $USDT, and $APE

ParaSpace v1 Features:

- Lending and Borrowing
- ERC-721 & ERC-20 Support
- $APE Staking via $APE Pool
- Liquidations

After ~3-4 weeks on mainnet, we will be rolling out the Buy Now, Pay Later and Marketplace features.
